title: #245 Squawking Twat
description:
Mark & Joe recap the red hot live pod with Nikki Glaser & Yannas Pappas before Joe tells us about Jason Kanter's hit & run incident in Tampa & Mark's trip to Minneapolis resulted in him working out in jeans and spilling liquid cheese all over himself! Check it out!
